---
// Hero.astro - Main hero section for the DISC paper landing page
---
<section id="hero" class="content-section hero-section">
  <div class="title-wrapper">
    <img src="/icon.png" alt="DISC icon" class="title-icon" />
    <h1 class="main-title" id="animated-title">DISC</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="subtitle" id="animated-subtitle">Dynamic Decomposition Improves LLM Inference Scaling</p>
  <p class="description">
    DISC adaptively partitions reasoning traces during inference so language models spend more compute on
    the most difficult steps. By subdividing challenging segments and prioritising their sampling,
    DISC delivers better solutions with fewer tokens across coding and math benchmarks.
  </p>

  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2502.16706" class="cta-button">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="button-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M4 1.5A1.5 1.5 0 012 3v10a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5h8A1.5 1.5 0 0013 13V5.621a1.5 1.5 0 00-.44-1.06L9.44 1.44A1.5 1.5 0 008.379 1H4zM8 1.75v3.5a.75.75 0 00.75.75h3.5" />
      </svg>
      <span class="button-text">Read the paper</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#results" class="secondary-link">Jump to results â†“</a>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-metrics">
    <div class="metric-card">
      <span class="metric-value">-5.0%</span>
      <span class="metric-label">pass@10 error on APPS</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <span class="metric-value">-6.7%</span>
      <span class="metric-label">pass@10 error on MATH500</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <span class="metric-value">-10.5%</span>
      <span class="metric-label">pass@10 error on LiveCodeBench</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="summary-grid">
    <div class="summary-card">
      <h3>Adaptive decomposition</h3>
      <p>Automatically adjusts step sizes at inference time, zooming in on pivotal reasoning pivots without handcrafted heuristics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <h3>Plug-and-play</h3>
      <p>Integrates with greedy, beam, or Monte Carlo tree search, controlling which prefixes receive more sampling budget.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <h3>Compute efficient</h3>
      <p>Allocates tokens to hard steps, improving sample and token efficiency across both proprietary and open-source LLMs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="resources-section">
    <div class="resources-buttons">
      <a href="/pdf/Dynamic_Decomposition_main.pdf" class="resource-button">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="resource-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8l-6-6z"></path>
          <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
          <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
          <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
        </svg>
        <span>Paper PDF</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/teaser.pdf" class="resource-button">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="resource-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 20l9-7-9-7-9 7 9 7z"></path>
          <line x1="12" y1="13" x2="12" y2="20"></line>
        </svg>
        <span>Teaser figure</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="diagram-placeholder">
    <iframe
      src="/teaser.pdf#toolbar=0&navpanes=0&scrollbar=0"
      title="DISC teaser diagram"
      class="diagram-doc"
      loading="lazy"
    ></iframe>
  </div>

  <div class="authors-section">
    <div class="authors-list">
      <p>
        <a href="https://jonathanmli.github.io/">Jonathan Li</a><sup class="affiliation-marker">1,2,4*</sup>,
        Wei Cheng<sup class="affiliation-marker">2</sup>,
        Benjamin Riviere<sup class="affiliation-marker">4</sup>,
        Yue Wu<sup class="affiliation-marker">3</sup>,
        Masafumi Oyamada<sup class="affiliation-marker">5</sup>
      </p>
      <p>
        Mengdi Wang<sup class="affiliation-marker">3</sup>,
        Yisong Yue<sup class="affiliation-marker">4</sup>,
        Santiago Paternain<sup class="affiliation-marker">1</sup>,
        Haifeng Chen<sup class="affiliation-marker">2</sup>
      </p>
      <p class="equal-contribution">
        <sup class="affiliation-marker">*</sup> Corresponding author
      </p>
      <p class="affiliations">
        <sup class="affiliation-marker">1</sup> Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <sup class="affiliation-marker">2</sup> NEC Laboratories America &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <sup class="affiliation-marker">3</sup> Princeton University &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <br>
        <sup class="affiliation-marker">4</sup> California Institute of Technology &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <sup class="affiliation-marker">5</sup> NEC Corporation
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .secondary-link {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2a2f6c;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .secondary-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .hero-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .metric-card {
    background: #f1f3f9;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2a2f6c;
  }

  .metric-label {
    color: #485065;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .summary-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(42, 47, 108, 0.12);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .summary-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #2a2f6c;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .summary-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #4a4d57;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .diagram-doc {
    width: min(100%, 900px);
    height: 540px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .affiliations {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    color: #6c757d;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-metrics,
    .summary-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(1, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .diagram-doc {
      height: 420px;
    }
  }
</style>
